  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Scoping market interventions to address the high cost of remittances in the Pacific</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This activity is a partnership with the Reserve Bank of New Zealand.&#xA0;MFAT is providing funding to establish a&#xA0;dedicated team within RBNZ to&#xA0;undertake a detailed design and scoping phase to identify options and recommendations for South Pacific Central Bank Governors and MFAT/RBNZ to consider as possible future investments in this area.</narrative>
